channel.desc: Action, Crime, Sci-Fi 1997 The FBI agent Sean Archer exchanges roles with the terrorist Castor with a face transplant surgery to get more information about his son's killer, but Castor uses the situation in his favor to implement his plan. John Travolta, Nicolas Cage, Joan Allen, Alessandro Nivola, Gina Gershon, John Woo, Mike Werb.
